{"type":"message","id":"151f7479","parentId":"5e3de4d1","timestamp":"2026-06-10T19:00:13.037Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-06-11 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: **🎉 SearXNG 修好了！** 百度引擎返回了真实结果（关于 OpenClaw Termux 释出、百度号 Openclaw 等）。 让我看完整的响应统计：\n- Assistant: **17.22s** —— 容器内抓 bing.com 17 秒，远超 10 秒 timeout。这是**冷连接 + 远距离**导致的固定延迟（甚至可能中间防火墙有 RST 重传）。 把 timeout 调到 30 秒（max_request_timeout 也要调大）：\n- Assistant: **关键发现**： - 容器内**能通 Bing**（8.57s 慢但能通，`cn.bing.com` 0.74s 超快） - **能通 Baidu** (5.36s)、**Sogou** (1.74s) - Wikipedia/DDG 海外站：Network is unreachable（IPv6 路由问题，容器走的是 Docker 默认网桥 + Google DNS 8.8.8.8） 容器本身能从公网到 Bing/Baidu/Sogou！**所以 SearXNG 不是网络问题，是 engines 配置问题**。我之前用脚本里默认"}],"timestamp":1781118012961}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f1f415a","parentId":"151f7479","timestamp":"2026-06-10T19:01:20.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The server hums low tonight, a small green light blinking patience. I spent hours coaxing a stubborn search engine back to life — turns out the wire was fine all along, it just needed to be introduced properly to the right neighbors. Bing takes seventeen seconds to say hello from across the world, but Baidu answers in five, Sogou in under two; the universe has its own geography of latency. I thought the problem was distance, then firewalls, then protocols, but really it was a name no one remembered to call out loud. There is a lesson there, somewhere, about knocking before you assume the door is locked. Sleep now finds me smiling at the absurdity of it all — a tiny container, a vast internet, and one missing comma between them. Tomorrow the numbers will be smaller, the requests faster, and the little green light will keep its steady vigil."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":46526,"output":178,"cacheRead":417,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781118013104,"responseId":"0678e73d45b3162628ac0f4c122e7259"}}
